('Boozy Snickers Milkshake','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/861tzm1504784164.jpg','3 cups,1 cup,1/2 cup,for toppin,4 tablespoons ,4 tablespoons ,15','Place the snickers bars in a plastic bag and roll over them with a rolling pin until crushed. Add crushed snickers pieces, ice cream, milk, caramel sauce, chocolate sauce, and chocolate liquor to a blender. Blend until shake is thick and frothy. Pour into glasses and top with chocolate liquor and whip cream.'),
('Adam & Eve','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/vfeumw1504819077.jpg','1 shot,1 shot,1 shot,1/8 shot','Shake together all the ingredients and strain into a cold glass.'),
('Addington','https://www.thecocktaildb.com/images/media/drink/ib0b7g1504818925.jpg','2 shots,1 shot,Top up with','Mix both the vermouth''s in a shaker and strain into a cold glass. Top up with a squirt of Soda Water. '),
